<i>adverb</i>: 어김없이 [어기멉씨], 또박또박 [또박또박] <br>
<ul style="list-style-type:square">
<li><i>adverb</i><br>
<dt>어김없이 [어기멉씨]</dt><br>
<dd>1. infallibly; punctually</dd><br>
<dd>약속 등을 어기는 일이 없이.</dd><br>
<dd>In a way that one does not break a promise, etc.</dd><br>
<dd>2. unerringly; definitely</dd><br>
<dd>틀림이 없이.</dd><br>
<dd>In a definite way with no doubt.</dd><br>
<dt>또박또박 [또박또박]</dt><br>
<dd>1. neatly; clearly</dd><br>
<dd>말이나 글씨 등이 분명하고 또렷한 모양.</dd><br>
<dd>In the manner that a remark or handwriting, etc., are clear and distinct.</dd><br>
<dd>2. regularly; punctually</dd><br>
<dd>규칙이나 차례 등을 한 번도 어기지 않고 지키는 모양.</dd><br>
<dd>In the manner of following a rule, order, etc., without violating it.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>